{"tid":693662,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】做日常無謂野 Day214 7/6","createTime":"2018-06-07T15:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T17:31:33.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d825fc7db03a8a431cc918d028b8b4d009294ee9","tid":693662,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=ANaRpzbWz%2BOUP63y54PQsTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=3c2eb1c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=ANaRpzbWz%2BOUP63y54PQsTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=87b5db3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"dccca263dce29cd5a3ecc31d6815f1898a4e1378","tid":693662,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:50:23.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae9d9023c8a181b892ec77300473b2a2af2c387","tid":693662,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7861fff3ea8f6f29390d3645a60c6f2d84b83d","tid":693662